    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick with a matching lid) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add your <strong>gnocchi</strong>,<strong> diced pepper </strong>and<strong> chopped tomatoes</strong> and cook for 8-10 min or until beginning to crisp and slightly char</p><p>Tip: Cooking for 4 or more? You may need 2 pans!</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
