    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, boil a kettle</p><p>Grate your <strong>cheddar cheese</strong> finely</p><p>Roll your <strong>lime[s]</strong> with your hand on a hard surface (to release more juice) and cut into 2 wedges per person</p><p>Trim, then slice your <strong>spring onion[s]</strong></p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p>",
